  <summary>Create and edit app shortcuts</summary>
  <developer_name translate="no">Fabrizio Alberio</developer_name>
  <developer id="io.github.fabrialberio">
    <name translate="no">Fabrizio Alberio</name>
  </developer>
  <description>
    <p>Pins allows you to customize your app menu by editing .desktop files.</p>
    <p>Some of the things you can do are:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>changing an app icon that doesn't fit in with your theme,</li>
      <li>creating custom shortcuts to websites,</li>
      <li>hiding apps you don't want to see,</li>
      <li>editing properties in .desktop files.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
